{"id":126295,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/11/以国税地税稽查迎接世界艾滋病日/","date":"2010-11-27T14:43:16Z","modified":"2010-11-27T14:43:16Z","title":"以国税地税稽查迎接世界艾滋病日","content":"<p><p><a href=\"http://www.zengjinyan.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/jc-004.jpg\" title=\"jc-004.jpg\"><img alt=\"jc-004.jpg\" src=\"http://www.zengjinyan.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/jc-004.thumbnail.jpg\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.zengjinyan.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/jc-003.jpg\" title=\"jc-003.jpg\"><img alt=\"jc-003.jpg\" src=\"http://www.zengjinyan.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/jc-003.thumbnail.jpg\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.zengjinyan.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/jc-002.jpg\" title=\"jc-002.jpg\"><img alt=\"jc-002.jpg\" src=\"http://www.zengjinyan.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/jc-002.thumbnail.jpg\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.zengjinyan.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/jc-002.jpg\" title=\"jc-002.jpg\"><img alt=\"jc-002.jpg\" src=\"http://www.zengjinyan.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/jc-002.thumbnail.jpg\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.zengjinyan.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/jc-001.jpg\" title=\"jc-001.jpg\"><img alt=\"jc-001.jpg\" src=\"http://www.zengjinyan.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/jc-001.thumbnail.jpg\" /></a><span>昨天接受国税询问，情况不太好，想不到今年以这样的方式迎接世界艾滋病日<2009-2010的主题（Universal Access &#038; Human Rights）>。中国特色的口号应该是：查税，为艾滋病家庭的关怀和救助纳税。</span><span></span> <span>致北京市朝阳区国税：</span><a href=\"http://www.zengjinyan.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/jc-003.jpg\" title=\"jc-003.jpg\"></a><a href=\"http://www.zengjinyan.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/jc-003.jpg\" title=\"jc-003.jpg\"></a><a href=\"http://www.zengjinyan.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/jc-004.jpg\" title=\"jc-004.jpg\"></a><a href=\"http://www.zengjinyan.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/jc-005.jpg\" title=\"jc-005.jpg\"></a></p>\n<p>2007-2009年爱源艾滋病关怀与救助工作资金往来单位如下：</p>\n<p>1.\tCAF（中华艾滋基金会）</p>\n<p>2.\tGFC（全球儿童基金会）</p>\n<p>3.\tUNICEF（联合国儿基会）（由中国性病艾滋病协会转账）</p>\n<p>4.\tITPC（联合基金）</p>\n<p>5.\t乐施会</p>\n<p>6.\tTIDES基金会</p>\n<p>7.\t个人通过PPC笔友俱乐部转账捐款给受艾滋病影响的孩子和家庭</p>\n<p>其中大部分是往来款，直接发放给受艾滋病影响的孩子和家庭，为他们提供生活、医疗和教育援助费用。作为企业收入的款项，已经如数缴纳营业税、所得税和各项杂税。我单位已经知会有资金往来的机构。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.zengjinyan.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/jc-004.jpg\" title=\"jc-004.jpg\"></a><a href=\"http://www.zengjinyan.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/jc-003.jpg\" title=\"jc-003.jpg\"></a></p></p>\n","author":138,"categories":[1],"tags":[8771]}